title: Ensoniq ASR-10 Covert Video Course DVD
description:
*ENSONIQ* -=Covert Videos Presents=- The ASR-10 Video Course

The ASR-10 Video Course by Covert Videos is a breakthrough in modern communications. It will take you from novice to expert! You will be able to handle the most important features of the ASR-10 with ease. Sequencing, Effects Routing, Sound and Sample Editing, will become your second language as you cruise through one of the most powerful and innovative sampling workstations ever created. 

Introduction

Enjoy and seed!
